%description
The package typesets Backus-Naur Form (BNF) definitions. It
creates aligned lists of productions, with numbers if required.
It can also print in-line BNF expressions using math mode.

%post
%{_sbindir}/texlive.post

%postun
if [ $1 -eq 0 ]; then
	%{_sbindir}/texlive.post
fi

